name: Accidental Landscape #1
description: Created (2011 JUN). Multi-color stripes visual was created from a power failure during a batch transfer of a few image files. All files cannot be opened nor restored except 3 of them with original content completely "repainted", creating 3 unique landscape that cannot be recreated by code. I have decided to mint 100 each generative artwork and released as a limited edition on Hic Et Nunc.
